{"tid":185321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"偷人Account呃人買iTunes卡嗰啲人不得好死! ! !","createTime":"2017-04-03T11:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T16:30:11.000Z","uid":7507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cd010ecbf5eb0b6ae8f5289166761e68e85dc083","tid":185321,"uid":7507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:23:59.000Z","msg":"是咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n家母就啱啱接觸LINE依個App, 點知佢朋友有日叫佢<br />\n<br />\n幫佢買住4張$1000蚊既iTunes卡話聽日比返錢佢 <br />\n<br />\n咁我娘親就見係朋友又冇防人之心咁on99幫佢買<br />\n左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係佢好彩唔係蠢得哂, 係條仆街叫佢比張卡既密碼<br />\n<br />\n佢個時, 家母開始知有啲野, 原來問返同事係佢同事比人<br />\n<br />\n偷左Account, 咁佢同事緊係唔認數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （咁我都明）<br />\n<br />\n屋企近日裝修已經冇哂錢, 1分錢都好重要, 依家又整<br />\n<br />\n單咁既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但係依家多左4張$1000嘅iTunes卡出<br />\n<br />\n嚟, 有冇好心人可以收留佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感激萬分!!!"},{"pid":"f7f4c48eae835d183aed35a6f079b94abbb47656","tid":185321,"uid":7507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:24:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d9b1f2d35fc3ae3ffd31a1556554790cb803b14","tid":185321,"uid":7507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:25:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fddcc70a6ff5e0240582791e97e21c77ecb8cf52","tid":185321,"uid":48235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:25:52.000Z","msg":"有冇得用黎買iPhone iPad 個d"},{"pid":"427e34709898c9451588f2e22a515f2663e82772","tid":185321,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T11:26:01.000Z","msg":"自己用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s